[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://git-wip-us.apache.org/repos/asf?p=lucene-solr.git;h=95d287e&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://git-wip-us.apache.org/repos/asf?p=lucene-solr.git;h=95d287e&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-11586&quot; title=&quot;Restored collection uses stateFormat=1 instead of 2&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SOLR-11586&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SOLR-11586&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Restored collection should use stateFormat=2 instead of 1&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16227491" author="jira-bot" created="Tue, 31 Oct 2017 20:37:26 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit ff6bf628310f88ea974c5b978d5e33221d58304a in lucene-solr&apos;s branch refs/heads/branch_7x from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=varun&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;varun&quot;&gt;varun&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://git-wip-us.apache.org/repos/asf?p=lucene-solr.git;h=ff6bf62&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://git-wip-us.apache.org/repos/asf?p=lucene-solr.git;h=ff6bf62&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-11586&quot; title=&quot;Restored collection uses stateFormat=1 instead of 2&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SOLR-11586&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SOLR-11586&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Restored collection should use stateFormat=2 instead of 1&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16233041" author="noble.paul" created="Wed, 1 Nov 2017 00:44:07 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Yes, we are eventually deprecating stateFormat=1&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16327813" author="varunthacker" created="Tue, 16 Jan 2018 21:13:30 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=noble.paul&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;noble.paul&quot;&gt;noble.paul&lt;/a&gt; I&apos;ve&#160;created&#160;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-11860&quot; title=&quot;Change the default state format to 2&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SOLR-11860&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SOLR-11860&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; to address that&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
